641.title: API returns 500 error on malformed JSON input
641.description: When sending malformed JSON to POST endpoints, the API returns a generic 500 error instead of a proper 400 Bad Request with validation details.

642.title: Add rate limiting to API endpoints
642.description: We need to implement rate limiting to prevent abuse of the API. Should support configurable limits per endpoint and per user.

643.title: Database connection pool exhaustion under load
643.description: Under high load conditions, the database connection pool gets exhausted causing timeouts. Need to tune pool size and implement connection recycling.

644.title: State vector simulation crashes for >20 qubits
644.description: Memory allocation fails when simulating circuits with more than 20 qubits. Need to implement sparse state vector representation.

645.title: Add support for parameterized gates
645.description: Implement support for parameterized quantum gates like RX, RY, RZ with arbitrary rotation angles.

646.title: Incorrect phase in CNOT gate implementation
646.description: The CNOT gate matrix has an incorrect global phase that causes issues with entanglement verification tests.

647.title: Circuit breaker not resetting after timeout
647.description: The circuit breaker stays in open state even after the timeout period has elapsed. The half-open state transition is not being triggered.

648.title: Add WebSocket support for real-time connections
648.description: Implement WebSocket proxying capability to support real-time bidirectional communication through the gateway.

649.title: Cache eviction not working for large payloads
649.description: Cache entries with large payloads are not being evicted properly, causing memory pressure. Need to implement size-based eviction.

650.title: Production outage - API returning 503
650.description: CRITICAL: Production API is returning 503 for all requests. Database connection pool exhausted. Immediate action required.

651.title: Add API documentation with Swagger/OpenAPI
651.description: We should add comprehensive API documentation using OpenAPI 3.0 specification. Low priority but would be helpful for developers.

652.title: Implement request timeout configuration
652.description: Allow configurable request timeouts for different API endpoints. Enhancement request from operations team.

653.title: Quantum decoherence simulation inaccurate
653.description: CRITICAL: The decoherence model produces results that deviate significantly from theoretical predictions for large qubit systems.

654.title: Add tutorial notebooks for beginners
654.description: Create Jupyter notebooks with step-by-step tutorials for quantum computing beginners.

655.title: Optimize matrix multiplication for sparse gates
655.description: Task to implement sparse matrix optimization for quantum gates with many zero elements.

656.title: Gateway crashes under high concurrent load
656.description: CRITICAL: Gateway process crashes when handling more than 10,000 concurrent connections. Stack trace attached.

657.title: Update README with deployment instructions
657.description: The README is missing Docker and Kubernetes deployment instructions. Low priority documentation update.

658.title: Implement request rate limiting per client
658.description: Feature request to add configurable rate limiting on a per-client basis to prevent abuse.
